import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['size'] = pd.to_numeric(data['size'], errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='size', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['size'].median(), color='red', label=f'Median: {data["size"].median():.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of the size of the nodes in the flare.json dataset?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

chart = plot(data)

chart = plot(data)
